    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚稀土矿商遭遇网络安全漏洞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/australian-rare-earths-miner-hit-by-cybersecurity-breach</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚稀土公司北方矿业有限公司 (Northern Minerals Ltd.) 表示，在该公司发现其网络安全保护措施遭到漏洞数月后，其部分数据被发布到“暗网”上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/australian-rare-earths-miner-hit-by-cybersecurity-breach</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 08:56:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国探月计划在月球表面留下爱国涂鸦</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/china-s-moon-mission-leaves-patriotic-graffiti-on-lunar-surface</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一艘中国航天器从月球背面升空，并在月球表面留下一些爱国涂鸦，标志着这次历史性的访问。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/china-s-moon-mission-leaves-patriotic-graffiti-on-lunar-surface</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 08:44:37 GMT</pubDate>
